<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include("components/head"); %>

<body class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">

<%- include("components/navbar"); %>

<div class="p-6 mt-6">
  <div class="p-3 flex justify-center items-center sm:text-6xl md:text-6xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-6xl">
    Kipify
  </div>
  <div class="flex justify-center items-center sm:text-2xl md:text-2xl lg:text-2xl xl:text-2xl">
    <div class="p-3 sm:w-3/5">
      Do you struggle with finding new music?
      Or finding music similar to what you listen to?
      Well we can help with that, we will make a playlist
      of 50 songs which we think you'll like.
      We analyse your Spotify data from the past to
      determine what you enjoy and what you don't.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex justify-center items-center sm:text-2xl md:text-2xl lg:text-2xl xl:text-2xl">
    <div class="p-3 sm:w-3/5">
      As of right now we provide two methods for
      recommendations, click&nbsp;
      <p class="inline-block bold text-green-500">
        Create
      </p>
      &nbsp;below and find the method which you like.
      If you don't want to login it's totally fine
      to just browse, however if you want us to create
      a playlist, you will have to login with your
      Spotify account
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="p-3 flex justify-center items-center sm:text-3xl md:text-3xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-3xl">
    <a class="p-3 border-2 border-white rounded-lg hover:bg-green-500 hover:border-green-500 hover:text-neutral-950"
      <% if (login) { %>
        href="/create"
      <% } else { %>
        href="/login?redirect=/create"
      <% } %>
    >
      Create
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>